o.<br>
<br>
Find a wizard and a mage same level (mid 30s at least) Find the deepest red mob a wiz can cast on then let the mage try it.  Mage won't be able to touch it with spells.<br>
<br>
This is really in the game Grim.  When I was lower level I tested it myself in sol B.<br>
<br>
